Subject: Queen Mary, University of London Tennis Club 
To: Peter
Content:
Queen Mary, University of London Tennis Club is the tennis club for Queen Mary, University of London, part of the University of London. Teams are currently entered in leagues run by the British Universities Sports Association. Monday night practice is held weekly in London Borough of Redbridge at an indoor facility housing carpet tennis courts. This facility is shared with University College London where along with Queen Mary, University of London home matches are played. Social tennis is run on Wednesday afternoon at Bethnal Green Park. 
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
